data.description: This 3 bed 2 bath home sits on a a large corner lot.  It features an enclosed covered front porch and a large living/entry room.  3 large bedrooms and 2 bath areas.  Kitchen/dinette area is spacious and there is an office area off the kitchen.  New roof in 2022.  First floor laundry. There is a detached single stall garage for storage and a partial basement for storage.  Great investment opportunity.
